These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, montecristo, blend, pall-mall
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, r&b, salsa, techno
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, manager, designer, coach
There 4 different types of food: carrot, eggplant, corn, kale
1. the manager is the fan of techno##1
2. the designer is between the blend-smoker and the pall-mall-smoker##2
3. the manager is the person eating carrot##1
4. the person eating kale is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the security-guard##1
6. the person eating corn is the blend-smoker##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
8. the security-guard is on the far right##1
9. the montecristo-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Cigar   | montecristo | pall-mall   | vegafina  | blend  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | techno    | metal      | salsa    |
| Job   | coach | manager | designer | security-guard |
| Food     | kale  | carrot       | eggplant    | corn     |

