.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, woodworking
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, orange, amber, aquamarine
4 different games are played: scrabble, bridge, whist, canasta
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, mechanic, photographer, manager
1. the manager is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
3. the person playing canasta is the mechanic##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person who likes aquamarine is between the person playing whist and the scientist##2
6. the manager is between the person who likes aquamarine and the person playing canasta##2
7. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1
8. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | drawing    | singing  | cooking    |
| Color   | purple      | orange  | aquamarine  | amber |
| Game           | canasta      | whist       | bridge      | scrabble       |
| Job         | mechanic    | manager | photographer | scientist |

