.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, daisy, begonia, rose
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, february, august, january
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, lawyer, paramedic, pilot
4 different games are played: billiard, go, snooker, scrabble
1. the paramedic is the person playing go##1
2. the person playing go is on the left of the pilot##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing go##1
4. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
5. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
6. the lawyer is the person who's birthday is in january##1
7. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
8. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in january##2
9. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who growsbegonia and the lawyer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Flower        | daisy | begonia     | daffodil   | rose     |
| Birthday       | february   | may   | august | january |
| Job         | analyst   | paramedic | pilot       | lawyer    |
| Game   | snooker    | go | billiard  | scrabble    |

