There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, juice, hot-chocolate, coffee
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, disco, electronic, techno
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, brown, green, blood-red
 1. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 2. the person who likes light-blue is on the far left##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person eating garlic##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who likes green##1
 5. the fan of techno is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 6. the person eating lemon is on the left of the fan of techno##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person drinking juice is the fan of disco##1
 9. the person eating lemon is between the person who likes blood-red and the fan of trance##2
10. the fan of electronic is the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | garlic         | lemon         | asparagus     | peach      |
| Beverage           | hot-chocolate | coffee | tea    | juice     |
| Music-Genre   | trance      | electronic       | techno    | disco       |
| Color         | light-blue     | green       | blood-red | brown |

