3. the person traveling to colone is between the person eating potato and the person traveling to liverpool##2
4. the librarian is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
5. the person traveling to colone is the person traveling to colone##1
6. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the analyst##1
8. the person who likes blood-red is on the far right##1
9. the person who likes orange is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | librarian | freelancer | analyst  | paramedic |
| Color   | orange      | yellow       | coral     | blood-red      |
| City   | miami   | liverpool      | colone   | edinburgh   |
| Food         | zucchini   | peach    | cauliflower | potato   |

